Package es.uam.eps.ir.relison.metrics.communities.graph.gini.edges.sizenormalized

Class SizeNormalizedCommunityEdgeGini<U>

java.lang.Object
es.uam.eps.ir.relison.metrics.communities.graph.gini.edges.sizenormalized.SizeNormalizedCommunityEdgeGini<U>
Type Parameters:
U - Type of the users.
All Implemented Interfaces:
CommunityMetric<U>
Direct Known Subclasses:
SizeNormalizedCompleteCommunityEdgeGini, SizeNormalizedInterCommunityEdgeGini, SizeNormalizedSemiCompleteCommunityEdgeGini
public abstract class SizeNormalizedCommunityEdgeGini<U>
extends java.lang.Object
implements CommunityMetric<U>
Computes the size normalized community edge Gini of the graph, i.e. the Gini coefficient for the number of edges in the graph, divided by the maximum number of possible links between the endpoint communities.
Author:
Javier Sanz-Cruzado (javier.sanz-cruzado@uam.es), Pablo Castells (pablo.castells@uam.es)
